  <brief_title>Safety/Efficacy Study of Drospirenone/Estradiol to Treat Postmenopausal Chinese Women With Vasomotor Symptoms.</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Multicenter Study Investigating the Efficacy and Tolerability of AngeliqÂ® (Drospirenone 2mg and Estradiol 1mg) in Postmenopausal Chinese Women With Vasomotor Symptoms Over Four 28-day Treatment Cycles.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
